accination-48\">Client is not due for IPV vaccination-48</a></td><td>Client is not due for IPV vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Not due\"</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client's|20age|20is|20more|20than|20or|20equal|20to|208|20weeks-40\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Client.39sageismorethanorequalto8weeks-40\">Client's age is more than or equal to 8 weeks-40</a></td><td>Client's age is more than or equal to 8 weeks</td><td><div><p>Today's date − \"Date of birth\" ≥ 8 weeks</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-Client|20is|20due|20for|20IPV|20vaccination-86\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-ClientisdueforIPVvaccination-86\">Client is due for IPV vaccination-86</a></td><td>Client is due for IPV vaccination</td><td><div><p>\"Immunization recommendation status\" = \"Due\" (where \"Type of poliovirus dose\" = \"IPV\")</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a name=\"IMMZD2DTPolioSequentialIPVbOPVVS-http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK-One|20poliovirus|20primary|20series|20dose|20was|20administered-130\"> </a><code>http://smart.who.int/immunizations/CodeSystem/IMMZDAK</code></td><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\">  <a href=\"CodeSystem-IMMZDAK.html#IMMZDAK-Onepoliovirusprimaryseriesdosewasadministered-130\">One poliovirus primary series dose was administered-130</a></td><td>One poliovirus primary series dose was administered</td><td><div><p>Count of vaccines administered (where \"Vaccine type\" = \"Poliovirus-containing vaccines\" and \"Type of dose\" = \"Primary series\") = 1</p>\n</div></td></tr><tr><td><a na